'''约翰·埃姆斯利'''（John Emsley，{{bd|1938年}}），[[英国|英国]]科普作家，专长为化学。曾为[[独立报|独立报]]《本月分子》专栏写了6年稿。
==科普图书==

*''Islington Green: A Book of Revelation'' 2012
*《构造大自然的基础材料》 ''Nature's Building Blocks: an A-Z Guide to the Elements'' 2001, 2nd edition 2011.
*《探寻物质之谜：创造健康、富足和可持续的世界》 ''A Healthy, Wealthy, Sustainable World'', Royal Society of Chemistry, 2010
*''Molecules of Murder'', Royal Society of Chemistry, 2008
*''Better Looking, Better Living, Better Loving'' Wiley-VCH 2007
*《致命元素：毒药的历史》 ''The Elements of Murder: a History of Poison'', Oxford University Press, 2005
*《虚荣心、生命力和生殖力》 ''Vanity, Vitality, and Virility'', Oxford University Press, 2004
*《磷元素令人震惊的历史》 ''Shocking History of Phosphorus'', 2000. US Edition ''The 13th Element: The Sordid Tale of Murder, Fire, and Phosphorus'', 2006
*''Was it something you ate?'', co-author P.Fell, Oxford University Press, 1999
*《分子探秘：影响日常生活的奇妙物质》 ''Molecules at an Exhibition'', Oxford University Press, 1998
*''The Elements'', 3rd edition, Oxford University Press, 1998
*《消费者化学制品指南》 ''The Consumer's Good Chemical Guide: Separating Facts from Fiction about Everyday Products'', W.H. Freeman, 1994.

